OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,FThe UK's biggest police force says it
OL,7,Fis still facing a #260 million budget
OL,8,Fshortfall and "substantial tough
OL,9,Fchoices" over cuts despite funding
OL,10,Fincreases from central and local
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,FMayor of London Sadiq Khan announced a
OL,14,F#10 million boost for the Met from
OL,15,FCity Hall and #73 million from central
OL,16,Fgovernment, giving the force total
OL,17,Ffunding of #1.159 billion for 2025/26.
