OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,FThis came after warnings from
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,8,FMark Rowley in December that the force
OL,9,Fhad a #450 million budget shortfall
OL,10,Fand could need to cut 2,300 officers
OL,11,Fand 400 staff. The force currently has
OL,12,Fjust more than 33,200 police officers
OL,13,Fand 11,200 staff.
OL,15,FLater that month, the Government
OL,16,Fpledged to increase funding for forces
OL,17,Facross England and Wales, but police
OL,18,Fchiefs warned there remained a #1.3
OL,19,Fbillion funding gap over the next two
OL,20,Fyears.
