OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the Met said while it was
OL,7,Fgrateful for the cash increases from
OL,8,Fthe Government and Mayor, it would
OL,9,Fstill have to make cuts to its
OL,10,Fservices and hoped the Government's
OL,11,Fspending review, when funding levels
OL,12,Fare announced in late spring, would
OL,13,Fsolve its problems.
OL,15,FA spokesperson said: "While this new
OL,16,Ffunding decreases our original funding
OL,17,Fgap from #450 million, it leaves us
OL,18,Fwith a #260 million shortfall and we
OL,19,Fwill have to make substantial tough
OL,20,Fchoices, reducing our size and
OL,21,Fservices.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
