OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,F"This will be hard for our dedicated
OL,7,Fofficers and staff, but equally will
OL,8,Fhave implications for policing London
OL,9,Fand we will communicate more in due
OL,10,Fcourse.
OL,12,F"We hope the upcoming spending review
OL,13,Fwill help fix our long-term funding
OL,14,Fissues and put us on a sustainable
OL,15,Ffooting for the future."
OL,17,FThe force could not provide revised
OL,18,Ffigures for the number of officers and
OL,19,Fstaff that it may need to cut.
