OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,FIn December, Sir Mark said there could
OL,7,Fbe cuts to the anti-robbery Flying
OL,8,FSquad and the removal of its firearms
OL,9,Fofficers; the Royal Parks Police could
OL,10,Fbe axed along with reductions to dogs
OL,11,Fand the mounted branch.
OL,13,FHe also warned of reduced opening
OL,14,Fhours for some police counters and a
OL,15,Freduction in the number of cold case
OL,16,Finvestigations looking at crimes
OL,17,Fcommitted "many years or decades ago".
OL,26,@yD@KOUyD@eO]
