OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,FThe forecast budget gap came after
OL,7,Funderfunded pay increases, the cost of
OL,8,Fmaintaining buildings, increased
OL,9,Fdemand on the service and a depletion
OL,10,Fof savings, he told the London
OL,11,FPolicing Board.
OL,13,FEven after the Government announced a
OL,14,Ffunding boost in December, the force
OL,15,Fsaid it would need to make the
OL,16,F"majority of the tough choices we have
OL,17,Fplanned for".
OL,19,FThe Mayor of London's office said the
OL,20,FMet is receiving an extra #320 million
OL,21,Fin 2025/26 compared to this year.
