OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,FSir Sadiq Khan said: "Bearing down on
OL,7,Fcrime and keeping Londoners safe is my
OL,8,Ftop priority as Mayor and I'll always
OL,9,Fuse all the levers at my disposal to
OL,10,Ffund the police, investing record sums
OL,11,Ffrom City Hall.
OL,13,F"I am pleased to propose an additional
OL,14,F#320 million since last year for the
OL,15,FMetropolitan Police, with #83 million
OL,16,Fmore since January, thanks to
OL,17,FGovernment support.
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@AOU
