OL,3,CBritain's biggest police force facing
OL,4,C'substantial tough choices' over cuts
OL,6,F"Despite this record-breaking
OL,7,Fadditional funding, the Met still
OL,8,Ffaces a difficult financial situation
OL,9,Fdue to over a decade of cuts by the
OL,10,Fprevious government.
OL,12,F"As Mayor, I will continue to work
OL,13,Fwith the new Government and the
OL,14,FCommissioner ahead of the forthcoming
OL,15,Fspending review on the funding the Met
OL,16,Fneeds to ensure we can continue
OL,17,Fbuilding a safer London for everyone."
